    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Collecting, processing, recycling, and disposing of discarded or excess equipment, products, or material in any form, including solids, oils, chemicals, liquids, and gases.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
